title: My Tee
overview: Mork is a grade-11 mischievous boy who sells porn DVDs at his father's barber shop. When his father is called out in the middle of a haircut, Mork decides to continue Tee's haircut and without doubt leaves Tee with a terrible haircut. Tee, who is extremely mad, is out for revenge and so the battle between Mork and Tee is on....
